  "detailed_description": "<strong>Mister Furry: Hot Muscles </strong> is <strong>unique </strong>furry horror with <strong>a deep plot</strong>, <strong>a lot of Muscular Mister Furries</strong>, <strong>Great Sound Effects</strong> and<strong> a Creepy Atmosphere of Muscular Furry Dungeon</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/4ae3bafae11f92a334a77debe05021f3.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This is the CENSORED Version</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1746979349\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/2d2de8abcde82fff26490a0e2ee058bc.avif?t=1746979349\" width=587 height=247 /></span><br>You are <strong>Playing </strong>the Game <strong>Mister Furry</strong> and you <strong>Dislike It</strong>, <strong>Anger </strong>and <strong>Swear </strong>at it, when Suddenly <strong>the Muscular Mister Furries</strong> <strong>Come to your Apartment</strong>, <strong>Punish You</strong>, <strong>Put You in a Cage</strong> and <strong>Send You to Their Dungeon</strong> ♂<br><strong>Collect </strong>the <strong>Hot Milk ♂</strong>, <strong>Dungeon's Items ♂</strong> and Complete <strong>the Side Quests</strong> to <strong>Get Out</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/d44dc8dc000b22d9510413e3aba445bb.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Features</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1746979349\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>♂ Muscular Mister Furries ♂</strong> - You cannot escape <strong>the Hard Punishment</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/4ae3bafae11f92a334a77debe05021f3.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>♂ Real Furry Dungeon ♂</strong> - Created by the precepts of <strong>the Dungeon Furry Master</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/8bbeed53ace4a6e7d453946e130ea244.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>♂ Gay Bar ♂</strong> - <strong>Visit Atmospheric Bar</strong> with <strong>Mister Furry</strong>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/cbfa4a390d5283bde84b2ad49cb5ccdd.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>♂ Mister Furry Gym ♂</strong> - Show 'em who is <strong>the Boss of this Furry Gym</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/9c43962c669d94f0174502b0bf1297b0.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>♂ Men Pool ♂</strong> - <strong>Swim Away</strong> from<strong> Mister Furry</strong> and <strong>Don't Lose Your Swimsuit</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/9d394028ebac20850718669425d9e61a.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><br></li><li> Collect <strong>18 Bottles with ♂ Hot Milk ♂</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/e551673a468d5e12e12359c64cd2a828.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><br></li><li> Steal <strong>♂ 5 Dungeon Items ♂</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/8bbeed53ace4a6e7d453946e130ea244.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>Atmospheric Music</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/f2d8e726425335e06511ec902b39ad5c.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/9744bbd3ae80f00f6dd7bd6b24b27b9e.avif?t=1746979349\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br>You will have to put a lot of mental and physical effort to beat up this game! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578220/extras/4ae3bafae11f92a334a77debe05021f3.webp?t=1746979349\" width=36 height=28 /></span><br><br>Will you be able to <strong>Escape Punishment</strong> from <strong>Mister Furry</strong>? ♂</h2>",
